# Setup {.unnumbered}

## Installing R and RStudio

You can download and install R/RStudio [from the posit website](https://posit.co/download/rstudio-desktop/).

## Data files

Commands to download the data files used in this course directly to your working directory will be provided during workshops.
Download buttons for the files also appear in this ebook when they are first introduced.
For convenience, the files are also provided below:
